# ThreadSanitizer suppressions for `just tsan`.
#
# crossbeam-deque's Chase-Lev deque synchronizes its buffer accesses
# with standalone SeqCst fences, which TSan does not model, so it
# reports Worker::push racing Stealer::steal_batch_and_pop. A known
# false positive (crossbeam-rs/crossbeam#589), previously masked
# because the global scheduler mutex serialized the surrounding code.
# Scoped to the crate so races in our own code still surface.
race:crossbeam_deque
